competition_group.name: Power Race
competition_group.rules:
Power Race is Team Power Ups monthly level competition. Each month we will have a different theme as we continue to grow.
Show off your Power-Up creating skills using the theme for each month!
Anyone can submit a Level for Power Race and enter the competition. Just add the Competition Tag with !addtags XXX-XXX-XXX Power Race, if the level shows up on this page, you're good to go.
